05:29.890 --> 05:31.590
No, you got it.

05:31.623 --> 05:32.857
No, I got it, okay.

05:32.889 --> 05:34.258
Okay, and don't forget
to bring the sign in.

05:34.290 --> 05:35.856
Okay, all right, I will.

05:36.887 --> 05:36.689
Yeah.

05:36.722 --> 05:37.522
Have fun.

05:37.555 --> 05:38.389
Bye.

05:39.789 --> 05:40.589
Bye, love you.

05:40.622 --> 05:41.689
Love you too.

05:41.722 --> 05:42.556
See you.

07:33.790 --> 07:38.790
As I live and breath,
Andrea Offerman is that you?

07:39.191 --> 07:40.557
I'll be damned.

07:40.590 --> 07:42.257
Penelope, I haven't
seen you since,

07:42.290 --> 07:43.289
