for like, 48 hours.

08:06.423 --> 08:08.891
But we'll see.

08:10.322 --> 08:12.323
Well, I super believe in you.

08:13.456 --> 08:15.891
What specifically did
you hate about uni?

08:16.823 --> 08:17.824
