08:23.857 --> 08:25.024
And I don't know if
you remember this

08:25.056 --> 08:27.522
but taking things
seriously is not my forte.

08:27.555 --> 08:29.356
It's not your
forte, that's right.

08:30.822 --> 08:31.890
Hate you.

08:31.923 --> 08:35.789
I told you so, but you totally
should have just stayed

08:35.823 --> 08:37.289
