09:32.956 --> 09:34.422
Okay, I will.

09:34.456 --> 09:39.457
Yeah, that sounds
great, full disclosure,

09:40.322 --> 09:42.389
I'm pretty high, right now.

09:42.422 --> 09:43.856
We know Hans.

09:45.355 --> 09:45.990
Okay, cool.

09:49.057 --> 09:51.724
So, how are we talking here?

09:53.323 --> 09:54.889
Three.

09:54.923 --> 09:57.522
Oh, it's not that bad.

09:57.555 --> 09:58.390
Out of three.

10:00.355 --> 10:02.223
Hey guys, how's it going?

10:02.957 --> 10:04.389
