12:04.490 --> 12:06.522
Did you just lose interest?

12:06.555 --> 12:09.456
I never really had
it, to be honest.

12:09.490 --> 12:12.756
Right, some good
parties at least?

12:12.790 --> 12:14.823
Yeah, there were a few of those.

12:14.856 --> 12:18.256
I don't know, even then it
was like people were tryna

12:18.289 --> 12:21.656
be something out of like,
an "American Pie" movie,

12:21.689 --> 12:23.389
or something.

12:23.423 --> 12:26.290
